had paid protection money to the California State 
Un-American Activities Committee. You could buy

20:21.806 --> 20:24.009
protection. A man named Hugh Burns was the state 
director, and he was given generous campaign

20:25.630 --> 20:31.757
contributions. And then he kept He

20:34.218 --> 20:40.427
prevented the Un-American Activities Committee 
