21:27.312 --> 21:28.153
that,

21:33.078 --> 21:41.590
to get around the real estate people who were 
trying to bring in the Federal Committee to get rid

21:33.078 --> 21:41.590
of not me, but get rid of the Bolsendorf and the 
whole gang of them. And for that matter, to attack

21:41.610 --> 21:49.061
the State Committee for taking payoffs to protect 
groups.

21:51.745 --> 21:52.847
That I knew nothing about. I had injured my kneecap 
in a television program with Mayor Bowen six weeks

21:52.867 --> 22:01.279
before that. of these long televised programs, 
