22:02.643 --> 22:11.493
of slums and talking about them to an audience. And 
he said, Frank, where is that one of the certain

22:12.635 --> 22:18.482
kind he particularly wanted to show? And it was in 
my briefcase across the room. And I

22:23.547 --> 22:27.452
hurried away from the camera to my briefcase to get 
that picture running back. And when I squatted

22:33.887 --> 22:39.453
down on my knee to get it, I split the cartilage into 
my kneecap. It's like football players get every

22:40.674 --> 22:43.277
weekend. You can almost get it with microsurgery 
nowadays, you can almost be back playing in six

22:44.498 --> 22:50.364
weeks. It was a little longer then. The housing 
authority, not telling me that they were bringing

22:52.507 --> 22:58.553
the Un-American Committee in on me, and yet 
feeling knowing i mean i had a marvelous record

23:00.693 --> 23:27.426
everybody i was very popular hundreds and 
hundreds of letters coming into the housing

23:00.693 --> 23:27.426
authority to defend me and the headlines for 30 
days in l.a were just wild headlines red plot to

23:00.693 --> 23:27.426
rule housing something like that and the housing 
authority said while we're working this thing all

23:27.760 --> 23:32.827
out, why don't you get your knee fixed? Because I 
was on salary, and I was suspended. So I checked

23:35.911 --> 23:48.208
into the Good Samaritan Hospital, Bolshevik 
