it. And we had that for six years. Now under 
Reagan's guidelines, they put hidden

26:44.226 --> 26:52.896
microphones into undercover agents to go into the 
churches Bible study classes in Arizona, in

26:53.416 --> 26:57.060
Tucson. The old trial there, sanctuary movement, 
